================================================================================
                      SafiServer Beta -- Safi Systems LLC
================================================================================

Configure and Install:
----------------------

     Initial configuration of the SafiServer can be preformed by running the 
	 install script:
	 
	      ./installserver.sh
		  
     The first time this script is ran; it will prompt you for the IP Address 
	 you want to bind the SafiServer to, the port to run the FastAGI server on, 
	 and the sa password for the SafiServer database.  To finish the install 
	 process run:
	 
		./installserver.sh start
	 
	 This will install and start the SafiServer service.
	 
	 Further configuration can be made from the SafiWorkshop (available for 
	 download at www.safisystems.com) or by changing the values in the 
	 resources/environment.properties config file.
	 
	 
Other command options
---------------------

	./installserver.sh start		#starts the SafiServer
	./installserver.sh stop		    #stops the SafiServer
	./installserver.sh console		#runs SafiServer in console mode
	./installserver.sh status		#displays the SafiServer service status
	
	
	